<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8"/>
	<title>小店激活</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no;" />
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="email=no" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/master.css" />
</head>
<body>
	<header>
		<a href="javascript:window.history.go(-1)" class="back">返回</a>
		<h1>小店激活</h1>
	</header>
	<section class="container">
		<div class="login register">
			<ul>
				<li><input type="tel" placeholder="请输入11位手机号" name="mobile" id="mobile" maxlength="11"/></li>
				<li class="message"><input type="text" placeholder="输入短信验证码" name="verificationCode" id="verificationCode"/><div id="getVerificationCode">获取验证码</div></li>
				<!-- <li><input type="password" placeholder="6-20位的登录密码" name="pwd" id="pwd"/></li> -->
			</ul>
			<div class="wrap">
				<a href="#" class="btn-red" id="btnRegister">激活</a>
				<a href="login.html" class="btn-white">我已激活，马上登录</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<div class="register-pop-ok hidden" id="register-ok">
		<div>
			<h4 class="color">&nbsp;恭喜您，激活成功！</h4>
			<p class="f-16 c-black">&nbsp;您可用拉卡拉的账号密码登录！ </p>
			<a class="btn-gray fl" href="forgetpassword.html">忘记密码</a>
			<a class="btn-red fr pop-login" href="login.html">登&nbsp;录</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="register-pop-ok hidden" id="register-already">
		<div>
			<p class="color">&nbsp;该手机号已激活，无需重复激活！</p>
			<a class="btn-red" href="login.html">登&nbsp;录</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="register-pop-ok hidden" id="register-psd">
		<div>
			<p class="color f-16">&nbsp;恭喜您，激活成功，请设置登录密码！</p>
			<input type="text" placeholder="6-20位的登录密码" id="pwd"/>
			<a class="btn-red" href="javascript:;" id="register-password">确&nbsp;认</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/lib/zepto.min.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common/setting.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common/common.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" id="platJs"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="cordova_plugins.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/accounts/register.js"></script>
</body>
</html>